					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You've got only 183 unique 16x16 areas. The reason to not go over 256 of any given structure (besides 8x8 tiles) is data size, not really difficulty. <br /><br />It's 256 8x8 tiles for the background, and 256 8x8 tiles for sprites. (Assuming no scanline stuff)</div>

					
